<div class="numismatics-search">
  <div class="numismatics-icon">
    <span class="icon-coin" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  </div>
  <div class="numismatics-text">
    <%= link_to "/numismatics" do %>
      <h3>Numismatics Search</h3>
    <% end %>
    <p>An updated search page for the Numismatic Collection to allow access by a variety of criteria to descriptions and images of Princeton University's comprehensive collection of coins, paper money, tokens, medals and decorations.</p>
